      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-02-17/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Feb 2017 18:05:02 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-02-17/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Clark to dismiss any staff involved in PharmaNet data breach&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The B.C. government has had several data breaches in recent years, in the Health Ministry and other departments, including in 2012, when the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/british-columbia/bc-investigating-unusual-activity-in-pharmanet-system/article34051936/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/british-columbia/bc-investigating-unusual-activity-in-pharmanet-system/article34051936/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;CrowdStrike Wins 2017 SC Award for Best Security Company and Best Behavior&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Satellite PR News (press release) IRVINE, Calif.()CrowdStrike, the leader in cloud-delivered endpoint protection, today announced that the company was recognized by the 2017 SC &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.satprnews.com/2017/02/16/crowdstrike-wins-2017-sc-award-for-best-security-company-and-best-behavior-analyticsenterprise-threat-detection-2/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.satprnews.com/2017/02/16/crowdstrike-wins-2017-sc-award-for-best-security-company-and-best-behavior-analyticsenterprise-threat-detection-2/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The Revenue Potential of Protecting Clients&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Whether malicious or unintentional, there is a trend of internal actors being the cause of data breaches. The obvious way to fix that problem is training &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://thevarguy.com/network-security-and-data-protection-software-solutions/revenue-potential-protecting-clients&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://thevarguy.com/network-security-and-data-protection-software-solutions/revenue-potential-protecting-clients&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Bill passed requiring Data Breach notification&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; to prepare to comply with Mandatory Data Breach Notification Laws, following the passage of the Privacy Amendment (Notifiable Data Breaches) Bill &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://idm.net.au/article/0011409-bill-passed-requiring-data-breach-notification&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://idm.net.au/article/0011409-bill-passed-requiring-data-breach-notification&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Application Performance Management (APM) Global Market Segmentation and&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;EIN News (press release) The concentration is on introducing SaaS approach into the Management System, efficient log management and the incorporation of predictive &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.einnews.com/pr_news/366994675/application-performance-management-apm-global-market-segmentation-and-major-players-analysis-and-forecast-to-2020&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.einnews.com/pr_news/366994675/application-performance-management-apm-global-market-segmentation-and-major-players-analysis-and-forecast-to-2020&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Lone Star Analysis Modeling Lowers Legal Risks&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The aim of the GDPR is to protect all EU citizens from &amp;ldquo;privacy and data breaches in an increasingly data-driven world.&amp;rdquo; Under the new regulations, &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.benzinga.com/pressreleases/17/02/p9058401/lone-star-analysis-modeling-lowers-legal-risks&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.benzinga.com/pressreleases/17/02/p9058401/lone-star-analysis-modeling-lowers-legal-risks&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Canada to Enact Legislation Will Require All Businesses to Report Data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Canada is in the final stages of enacting legislation that will require all companies to report data breaches to the federal government.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.tripwire.com/state-of-security/latest-security-news/canada-to-enact-legislation-will-require-all-businesses-to-report-data-breaches/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.tripwire.com/state-of-security/latest-security-news/canada-to-enact-legislation-will-require-all-businesses-to-report-data-breaches/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Rule on records for substance use disorder patients is delayed&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;hellip; IT such as EHRs, mobile apps and patient portals, given recent high-profile data breaches and a perceived lack of privacy protections by providers.  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.healthdatamanagement.com/news/rule-on-records-for-substance-use-disorder-patients-is-delayed&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.healthdatamanagement.com/news/rule-on-records-for-substance-use-disorder-patients-is-delayed&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo-Verizon Deal Nearly Done But Verizon Lowers Offer By $250 to $350&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Marshalltown Data breaches really hurt, and Yahoo is reminded of that reality at the negotiating table. Verizon has been renegotiating the acquisition deal with the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.themarshalltown.com/yahoo-verizon-deal-nearly-done-but-verizon-lowers-offer-by-250-to-350-million-report/21951&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.themarshalltown.com/yahoo-verizon-deal-nearly-done-but-verizon-lowers-offer-by-250-to-350-million-report/21951&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Arby&amp;rsquo;s Data Breach Exposes 350000 Records; 2017 Total Leaps Above 1 Million&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The latest count from the Identity Theft Resource Center (ITRC) reports that there have been 144 data breaches recorded this year through February &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://247wallst.com/technology-3/2017/02/17/arbys-data-breach-exposes-350000-records-2017-total-leaps-above-1-million/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://247wallst.com/technology-3/2017/02/17/arbys-data-breach-exposes-350000-records-2017-total-leaps-above-1-million/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;United States: March 1 Is Deadline For Small Breach Notifications Under&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mondaq News Alerts (registration) HIPAA covered entities that suffered &amp;ldquo;small&amp;rdquo; data breaches in calendar year 2016 have until March 1, 2017 to report the breach to the U.S. Department &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.mondaq.com/unitedstates/x/569534/Healthcare/March+1+Is+Deadline+For+Small+Breach+Notifications+Under+HIPAA&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.mondaq.com/unitedstates/x/569534/Healthcare/March+1+Is+Deadline+For+Small+Breach+Notifications+Under+HIPAA&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Having cyber insurance cover can help businesses handle data breaches, says&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Out-Law.com The cyber insurance market in the UK is still relatively nascent, but forthcoming changes to EU legislation, including the introduction of the EU General &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.out-law.com/en/articles/2017/february/having-cyber-insurance-cover-can-help-businesses-handle-data-breaches-says-expert/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.out-law.com/en/articles/2017/february/having-cyber-insurance-cover-can-help-businesses-handle-data-breaches-says-expert/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Clavister Launches Innovative Endpoint Protection Solution&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Clavister, a leader in high-performance network security, has launched a new endpoint security solution to protect devices including desktop and &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.channelemea.com/spip.php?article39031&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.channelemea.com/spip.php?article39031&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Businesses need to prioritise security in &amp;lsquo;Open Economy&amp;rsquo;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With GDPR legislation coming into force in 2018, it is vital that businesses are thinking about the potential impact of future data breaches now and how &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.eastmidlandsbusinesslink.co.uk/mag/news/business-prioritise-security-open-economy/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.eastmidlandsbusinesslink.co.uk/mag/news/business-prioritise-security-open-economy/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Fallout at Arby&amp;rsquo;s  data breaches a matter of &amp;lsquo;when&amp;rsquo; not &amp;lsquo;if&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Unions, called the ongoing waves of retail data breaches a national &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://news.retailrisk.com/news/fallout-at-arbys-data-breaches-a-matter-of-when-not-if/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://news.retailrisk.com/news/fallout-at-arbys-data-breaches-a-matter-of-when-not-if/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Yahoo Explains Cookie Forgery Related To Two 2016 Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Yahoo has provided further clarification on the cookie forging activity related to data breaches disclosed in September and December of last year.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/yahoo-explains-cookie-forgery-related-to-two-2016-breaches/d/d-id/1328205&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.darkreading.com/attacks-breaches/yahoo-explains-cookie-forgery-related-to-two-2016-breaches/d/d-id/1328205&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Users take the cheese to solve data breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cheese Movers International&amp;rsquo;s restructuring resulted in some employees being unhappy with either their new role or the new management.  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.csoonline.com/article/3170895/security/users-take-the-cheese-to-solve-data-breaches.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.csoonline.com/article/3170895/security/users-take-the-cheese-to-solve-data-breaches.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;OCR rocks Memorial Healthcare System with $5.5M fine&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The healthcare organization was cited for lapses in auditing employee access to protected health information, resulting in data breaches affecting &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.healthdatamanagement.com/news/ocr-rocks-memorial-healthcare-system-with-55m-fine&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.healthdatamanagement.com/news/ocr-rocks-memorial-healthcare-system-with-55m-fine&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Health data breaches and hacker attacks spiked dramatically in 2016&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Health data breaches triggered by hacking attacks spiked by 320% in 2016 and ransomware became widespread, according to a report by a health IT &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://searchhealthit.techtarget.com/blog/Health-IT-Pulse/Health-data-breaches-and-hacker-attacks-spiked-dramatically-in-2016&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://searchhealthit.techtarget.com/blog/Health-IT-Pulse/Health-data-breaches-and-hacker-attacks-spiked-dramatically-in-2016&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

